Ndaka dzikinurwa, Svondo yapfuura, apo munhu wa Mwari aive achiita Munamato we vazhinji.

0:02:15.440,0:02:25.920
Akanga achingonyengetera kune mweya yose yakaipa inokonzera zvipingidzo ne zvipingamupinyi.

0:02:25.920,0:02:29.000
Takatanga kunyengetera munyengetero iwowo pamwe chete nomu Porofita T.B. Joshua.

0:02:29.000,0:02:33.900
Pakarepo, pandakanga ndichinyengetera ndiri kumashure, ndakazviwana ndiri pasi, ndichidanidzira.

0:02:33.900,0:02:36.020
Ndaida kubvisa nguo dzangu!

0:02:36.020,0:02:39.640
Panguva yandakazoziva, ndakazviwana ndiri paatari.

0:02:39.640,0:02:48.560
Zvose zvakatanga musi wa December 25, 2004, pandakanga ndiri kuchikoro.

0:02:48.560,0:02:55.560
Shamwari dzangu dzakaenda neni kune kirabhu umo vanhu vaiputa ne kunwa.

0:02:55.560,0:02:58.080
Vakandibvunza kana ndaizosvuta.

0:02:58.080,0:03:06.220
Ndakavaudza kuti ndakanga ndisati ndambosvuta uye kuti baba vangu havana kumbosvuta kana kunwa, saka sei ndaizotanga kusvuta?

0:03:06.220,0:03:09.060
Ivo vakati ndaifanira kukanganwa nezvazvo nokuti ndakanga ndiri kuchikoro

0:03:09.060,0:03:12.600
Uye vabereki vangu vakanga vasineni - ndaifanira kusvuta.

0:03:12.600,0:03:14.960
Kubvira ipapo, ndakatanga kusvuta.

0:03:14.960,0:03:21.520
Mushure mokunge ndasvuta, ndakatanga kutora zvinodhaka zvakanyanya uye kunwa doro.

0:03:21.520,0:03:31.460
Rimwe zuva, shamwari yangu yakanditora kune imwe nzvimbo yaiva ne nhengo dzechikwata.

0:03:31.460,0:03:34.720
Panzvimbo iyoyo, apo nhengo dzechikwata dzaive dzakaungana,

0:03:34.720,0:03:44.380
Akaudza nhengo kuti aida kundipinza muchitendero chavo.

0:03:44.380,0:03:53.060
Ndakati ndakanga ndisingadi kubatanidzwa asi vakandimanikidza, vakandipa doro ndokubva ndadhakwa.

0:03:53.060,0:03:59.600
Zvadaro, vakandirova zvakanyanya ndokundipa chimwe chinhu kuti ndimedze.

0:03:59.600,0:04:04.700
Pashure, vakandiudza kuti hapana munhu aifanira kuziva kuti ndakanga ndiri nhengo yechitendero.

0:04:04.700,0:04:11.480
Zuva rakatevera, shamwari yangu yakandidana ikati vaida kuenda kuno 'kumushando'.

0:04:11.480,0:04:15.100
Akandibvunza kana ndaizoenda navo kune mushando wacho, ndakati kwete.

0:04:15.100,0:04:21.900
Akataura kuti chakanga chiri chisungiro changu chekuti ndiende uye kana ndisina kuenda, vaisazondiona sechinhu chipi nechipi.

0:04:21.900,0:04:26.040
Saka, ndakaenda navo uye vakandipa pfuti.

0:04:26.040,0:04:28.740
Takaenda kunoita basa racho.

0:04:28.740,0:04:43.680
Takaenda mukamuri yaiva nevakadzi, takatora zvishongo zvose , ma foni avo nezvose zvavaiva nazvo, ndokubva tabva.

0:04:43.680,0:04:47.940
Iwe unoreva kuti vamwe vako vakakudana iwe uye mose ndokuenda kuno dii?

0:04:47.940,0:04:49.360
Takaenda kunoba.

0:04:49.360,0:04:51.040
Zvakanaka, kuba? Ehe.

0:04:51.040,0:05:03.140
Apo takaenda, takaita zvisina kufanira ku madzimai avo vaisada kutipa mari yavo kana cheni dzavo,

0:05:03.140,0:05:05.300
Ipapo vaizotipa mari yavo uye taivarega vachienda.

0:05:05.300,0:05:11.040
Patakadzoka, taizopa zvinhu zvataba kune murume mukuru mukuru muchitendero.

0:05:11.040,0:05:15.380
Izvozvo ndizvo zvaive kutanga kwe chitendero ichi kwandiri.

0:05:15.380,0:05:19.240
Zvakandibata zvakanyanya.

0:05:19.240,0:05:26.960
Panguva iyoyo, ndakanga ndisina matatuu ose aya pamuviri wangu.

0:05:26.960,0:05:33.620
Nokuti ndakanga ndave nhengo yechitendero, ndakatanga kuwana matatuu ose aya.

0:05:33.620,0:05:35.940
Tarisai pasikirini yeTV yenyu.

0:05:35.940,0:05:44.140
Mukoma wedu ari kupupura kuti mweya yakaipa iyi yakamutambudza sei muhupenyu hwake hwose, kusvika pekufunga

0:05:44.140,0:05:47.080
kuisa matatuu pamuviri wake wese.

0:05:47.080,0:05:50.120
Ari pano kuzotitaurira chaizvozvo zvinoreva matatuu ose aya.

0:05:50.120,0:05:53.500
Unogona kutsanangura here kuti wakawana sei ma tatuu aya uye kuti anorevei?

0:05:53.500,0:06:02.820
Pa tatuu riri pamutsipa wangu,

0:06:02.820,0:06:14.160
Chero nhengo yeboka rangu rekare akaiona, anobva aziva kuti ndaive nhengo.

0:06:14.160,0:06:16.100
Tarisa pa sikirini ye TV.

0:06:16.100,0:06:25.960
Tamunzwa achitsanangura - ati iyo iyo tatuu ye pamutsipa wake ndiyo tatuu yekuzivikanwa nayo, inoratidza kuti iye

0:06:25.960,0:06:29.820
inhengo ye boka rechitendero chakavanzika.

0:06:29.820,0:06:38.740
Pandakatanga kunyora matatuu ose aya, zvakakanganisa hupenyu hwangu zvakashata.

0:06:38.740,0:06:48.000
Dzimwe nguva, mweya waindisundira kuenda kundosvuta uye kupamba.

0:06:48.000,0:06:52.880
Kunyanya iyi tatuu iri padyo neziso rangu.

0:06:52.880,0:06:55.600
Kana ndichinge ndisina mari, maziso angu aizotsvuka.

0:06:55.600,0:06:59.520
Ndaizotanga kutsvaka mari yekuti nditenge zvinodhaka.

0:06:59.520,0:07:01.600
Tatuu riri paziso rinorevei?

0:07:01.600,0:07:03.920
Iyi 'misodzi yomufaro'.

0:07:03.920,0:07:05.240
Zvakanaka, iwe unoti 'misodzi yomufaro'?

0:07:05.240,0:07:05.860
Hongu.

0:07:05.860,0:07:08.080
Chaizvoizvo misodzi yomufaro here?

0:07:08.080,0:07:12.900
Kwandiri, hazvirevi misodzi yemufaro asi misodzi yekusuwa.

0:07:12.900,0:07:18.020
Nokuti ndaitora chimwe chinhu chisiri changu nechisimba.

0:07:18.020,0:07:20.660
It means sorrow to me.

0:07:20.660,0:07:22.160
Unoreva kuti, 'misodzi yekusuruvara'?

0:07:22.160,0:07:22.660
Hongu.

0:07:22.660,0:07:28.660
Nokuti unofamba uchifurufusha vanhu, uchitora zvinhu zvavo ne chisimba?

0:07:28.660,0:07:42.140
Kunyangwe apo baba vangu vaitaura neni, havakwanisa kunditarisa mumaziso angu, ndaizotsamwa.

0:07:42.140,0:07:48.060
Pandairwisana neshamwari dzangu, kusvikira ndaona ropa, maziso angu asati adzika pasi.

0:07:48.060,0:07:52.540
Zvakanaka, munguva yehupupuriro hwako iwe wati waifarira kutora zvinhu kubva kuvanhu ne chisimba.

0:07:52.540,0:07:54.720
Unorevei naizvozvo?

0:07:54.720,0:08:03.540
Kuba mari dzevanhu - Ndaizoshandisa zvose zvandaive nazvo kuti ndiwane mari ne chisimba.

0:08:03.540,0:08:05.580
Ndezvipi zvombo zvawaishandisa?

0:08:05.580,0:08:12.820
Taishandisa mapanga, pfuti uye dzimwe nguva, taizoshandisa miti sekunge yaiva pfuti.

0:08:12.820,0:08:14.960
Enderera mberi.

0:08:14.960,0:08:26.640
Apo ndaiuya kumba, vanin'ina vangu  vaizondiona ndichisvuta uye ndichinwa.

0:08:26.640,0:08:32.520
Mweya iwoyo wakavapinda uye zvino, vari kusvuta kunyangwe kupfuura ini.

0:08:32.520,0:08:40.200
Ndakanga ndisisina nzira yekuvadzora, ini ndini mukuru mumba medu.

0:08:40.200,0:08:49.800
Nzira yandayaita, vaidzidza kubva kwandiri; Iko zvino, ndakadzikinurwa, ndavekuona kuti zvinhu izvi hazvina kunaka.

0:08:49.800,0:08:55.440
Apo ndinoona vanin'ina vangu vachiputa uye kunwa zvino ndirwadza zvikuru nokuti zvinoparadza;

0:08:55.440,0:08:59.080
Hazviite kuti munhu aende mberi asi zvino mudzosera kumashure.

0:08:59.080,0:09:05.480
Zvakanaka, ungatiudza kuti mweya yakaipa iyi yakakanganisa sei ukama hwako nemudzimai wako?

0:09:05.480,0:09:17.120
Dzimwe nguva, pandaienda kunze, apo ndaidzoka, mudzimai wangu aizondibvunza

0:09:17.120,0:09:23.560
chikonzero nei ndaienda kunonwa nekuti zvakanga zvisina kunaka, ndaifanira kufunga nezve pamuviri paaive napo.

0:09:23.560,0:09:27.560
Ndaingomutarisa nekutsamwa ndotanga kumurova zvakanyanya.

0:09:27.560,0:09:33.040
Pane imwe nguva yandakamurova kusvika pamwero wekuti ropa rakatanga kubuda richibva maari.

0:09:33.040,0:09:40.040
Iwe unoreva here dhimoni raitambudza hupenyu hwako rakaita kuti urove mudzimai wako, kunyange paaive nepamuviri?

0:09:40.040,0:09:42.320
Hungu, ndaiwanzomurova.

0:09:42.320,0:09:47.680
Chero chinhu chipi nechipi cha aitaura, kunyange dai chaiva chiduku kwazvo mweya iwoyo waizo

0:09:47.680,0:09:51.000
pinda mandiri wondiudza kuti ndirove mudzimai wangu uye ndimuuraye.

0:09:51.000,0:09:58.620
Ndaizo mudzvanya mutsipa wake, kusvikira vabereki vangu vaiuya kuzomununura kubva paruoko rwangu.

0:09:58.620,0:10:02.860
Unoreva kuti iwe wakamurova kusvika ave kubuda ropa apo aive nepamuviri?

0:10:02.860,0:10:04.140
Hongu.

0:10:04.140,0:10:06.920
Iwe hauna kumboita nyadzi nazvo here?

0:10:06.920,0:10:13.840
Yaiva nguva iyoyo, handina kumbozvidemba asi ikozvino ndakadzikinurwa, handicharova mudzimai wangu zvakare.

0:10:13.840,0:10:14.620
Zvakanaka, imbo mira.

0:10:14.620,0:10:17.780
Tisati taenda kune zvakaitika kwauri mushure mekudzikinurwa kwako, tine mibvunzo yatinoda kukubvunza.

0:10:17.780,0:10:19.620
Ngatiuyei kuna amai vako na baba vako.

0:10:19.620,0:10:24.540
Ko mweya uyu wakaipa wakakanganisa sei hukama hwako namai vako nababa vako?

0:10:24.540,0:10:33.680
Mweya wakaipa wakakanganisa bhizimisi raamai vangu nekuda kwezvinhu zvandakanga ndichiita,

0:10:33.680,0:10:37.320
Vaizondidana kuti vandibvunze kuti sei ndaive ndichiita zvinhu zvose izvi.

0:10:37.320,0:10:41.620
Ndakatomboenda kune imwe nzvimbo kuti ndiisire baba vangu mushonga.

0:10:41.620,0:10:44.880
Kuitira kuti ani naani anoda kubatsira baba vangu atadze kuvabatsira.

0:10:44.880,0:10:54.440
Ndakaita izvozvo nekuda kwezuva ravakadana mapurisa kuti vazondisunga.

0:10:54.440,0:11:01.280
Ichi ndicho chikonzero nei ndakazviita - kuti vaisazowana rubatsiro kubva kupi zvako

0:11:01.280,0:11:05.520
Zvakanaka, iwe ungangotiudza kuti chii chakaita kuti baba vako vaite izvi?

0:11:05.520,0:11:06.820
Wanga uri kuitei nababa vako?

0:11:06.820,0:11:09.540
Tiudzei kuti mweya wakaipa uyu wakakanganisa ukama hwako nababa vako sei.

0:11:09.540,0:11:13.920
Ndakange ndisinga varemekedze; ndisingavaone sa baba vangu.

0:11:13.920,0:11:19.600
Kusvika pakuti kana vaida kundirova, ndaivabata ndichida kuvarwisa.

0:11:19.600,0:11:25.760
Izvo zvakaunza kusanzwisisana pakati pa amai vangu nababa.

0:11:25.760,0:11:34.940
Baba vangu vakati vaizondiramba uye ini handizini ndega mwanakomana wavaiva naye.

0:11:34.940,0:11:46.840
Asi amai vangu havana kubvumirana nazvo izvi ndizvo zvose zvakaitika

0:11:46.840,0:11:50.160
Zvakanaka. Iye zvino, tinogona here kuuya kune apo wakadzikinurwa?

0:11:50.160,0:11:52.660
Wakazoziva sei pamusoro pezve SCOAN?

0:11:52.660,0:11:54.900
Uye pawakasvika - tiudze zvakaitika kwauri.

0:11:54.900,0:11:57.480
Amai vangu ndivo vakandimanikidza kuuya ku SCOAN!

0:11:57.480,0:12:04.960
Svondo yapfuura, pandakanga ndiri muchechi, mweya wakaipa wakandiudza kuti ndinofanira kuenda ndokubva ndazviita.

0:12:04.960,0:12:12.500
Pandakabva, amai vangu vakanga vachinditsvaka pose, saka vakatumira munin'ina wangu kuti anditsvage.

0:12:12.500,0:12:16.540
Munun'ina wangu akandiona ndokundidana kuti ndipinde mukati zvakare; Pandakadzoka,

0:12:16.540,0:12:23.140
Mweya waindisundidzira kuti ndibude kuti ndinoputa, uchindibvunza kuti sei ndaive muchechi.

0:12:23.140,0:12:27.520
Pandakadzoka, amai vangu vakanditsamwira ndokundibvunza kuti nei ndakabuda.

0:12:27.520,0:12:31.060
Handina kumbo vapindura.

0:12:31.060,0:12:36.060
Munguva ye Munyengetero we Vazhinji, handizive chakauya pamusoro pangu.

0:12:36.060,0:12:42.820
Pakanga pane chimwe chinhu chakafanana nemoto chakanga chiri kupisa mukati mangu, saka ndaida kubvisa nguo dzangu!

0:12:42.820,0:12:50.700
Ndaida kutiza asi ndakanzwa ndakasungirirwa pasi; Mweya wa Mwari hauna kunditendera kuti ndibude.

0:12:50.700,0:12:57.300
Pakupedzisira, ndakawira pasi ndikazviona ndave kuatari.

0:12:57.300,0:13:02.980
Zvakanaka, iwe unogona kutiudza - kubva panguva yawakadzikinurwa - chii chauri kucherechedza kuti chachinja muupenyu hwako

0:13:02.980,0:13:05.780
Uye mune ukama nemhuri yako?

0:13:05.780,0:13:10.440
Zvino, ndinoda mudzimai wangu; Isu tave kuwirirana.

0:13:10.440,0:13:16.920
Handisisiri kufambidzana neshamwari, ndakatotsemura kadhi rangu SIM re foni yangu, saka shamwari idzodzo dzakaipa hadzigoni kundifonera zvakare.

0:13:16.920,0:13:17.940
Handiendi kunze kumafaro.

0:13:17.940,0:13:23.220
Kana amai vangu vachitaura neni zvino, ndinogara ndichivateerera.

0:13:23.220,0:13:27.300
Iyi tatuu iri paruoko rwangu, ndaisi shandisa kuti ndinyengedze vakadzi.

0:13:27.300,0:13:35.520
Dzimwe nguva, ndaitora mudzimai kunze, ndichimuudza kuti ndaida kumubatsira.

0:13:35.520,0:13:43.080
Ndaizomutora ku hotera uye aizofunga kuti ndini ndega chete aida kurara naye

0:13:43.080,0:13:45.620
Asi pataisvika ku hotera, taizomupa madhiragi.

0:13:45.620,0:13:49.480
Iye aisazoziva kuti chii chiri kuitika, boka redu rese raizo rara naye.

0:13:49.480,0:13:54.340
Iyi tatuu musoro wegondo.

0:13:54.340,0:13:57.060
Zvakanaka, musoro wegondo?

0:13:57.060,0:14:01.620
Sezvo ndakadzikinurwa, handisisiri kusvuta zvakare.

0:14:01.620,0:14:06.780
Zuva randaka dzikinurwa, ndakarota.

0:14:06.780,0:14:10.660
Ndakaona shamwari dzangu munzvimbo yavakanga vachiputa.

0:14:10.660,0:14:16.520
Vakandidaidza kuti ndisvute navo ndikaenda.

0:14:16.520,0:14:19.560
Ndakakweva fodya kamwe ndo kukweva kechipiri;

0:14:19.560,0:14:24.940
pakukweva ke chitatu, ndakanga ndave kuda kukweva, chimwe chinhu chakatanga kubuda mumhuno dzangu.

0:14:24.940,0:14:28.340
Ipapo, izwi rakandiudza kuti nditarise kuruboshwe kwangu.

0:14:28.340,0:14:34.340
Pandakatarisa kuruboshwe rwangu, ndakaona vanhu vemunyika, saka ndakatarisa kurudyi rwangu

0:14:34.340,0:14:37.960
Ndakaona muPorofita T.B. Joshua akabata ruoko rwangu.

0:14:37.960,0:14:48.760
Vakabata ruoko rwangu, muPorofita T.B. Joshua akaenda neni mukamuri umo vanhu vaiimba nziyo dzokurumbidza.

0:14:48.760,0:14:52.520
Umwe munhu aive agere pachigaro cheushe uye pakanga pane chiedza.

0:14:52.520,0:14:59.200
Ndakabvunza munhu wa Mwari kana ndaigona kuona munhu akange akagara pachigaro cheushe.

0:14:59.200,0:15:05.080
Akandibvunza kana ndaiva nemaziso ekuona uye kana Mwari akandipa maziso kuti ndione munhu uyu ndaizokwanisa kumira here?

0:15:05.080,0:15:07.180
Ndakati ndaida kuona munhu wacho.

0:15:07.180,0:15:10.440
Zvadaro, ndakanzwa inzwi guru richibva pachigaro cheushe.

0:15:10.440,0:15:14.000
Rakati, "Christian, unoziva zvinorehwa kuve mu Kristu here?"

